Features: Dynamic RGB Lighting 
Illuminate your system with dynamic ten-zone RGB lighting with individually addressable RGB LEDs encased in a panoramic light pipe that offers unobstructed viewing from virtually every angle.

Create and Customize 
Choose from dozens of preset lighting profiles, or create your own in CORSAIR iCUE software.

Optimized for AMD Motherboards 
Achieve top bandwidth and tight response times on the latest AMD DDR4 motherboards to complement your cutting-edge Ryzen system.

Dual-Tone Aluminum Heatspreader 
Conducts heat away from your memory for superb cooling even when overclocked, with distinctive dual-tone styling to complement your system build.

Maximum Speed Boost 
Automatically configures to maximum supported speed on compatible systems for faster load times, multitasking, and more right out of the box - no need to set in BIOS.

Custom Performance PCB 
Provides the highest signal quality for the greatest level of performance and stability.

Tightly Screened Memory 
Carefully screened memory chips for extended overclocking potential.

Unite Your Setup 
Take control with CORSAIR iCUE software and synchronize lighting with other CORSAIR RGB products across the iCUE ecosystem.
